print('To find relationsip between feature and label')
x=df.drop(columns=['sales'])
y=df.sales
plt.figure(figsize=(20,20),facecolor='blue')
plotno=1
for columns in x:
    if plotno<=5:
        ax=plt.subplot(2,3,plotno)
        sns.stripplot(x=y,y=x[columns],hue=y)
        plt.xlabel('sales', fontsize=15)
        plt.ylabel(columns, fontsize=15)
    plotno+=1
plt.show()
